data.description: Beautifully refreshed 4-bedroom home in one of Mojave's sought-after neighborhoods. It boasts all new carpet in the bedrooms, with a mixture of tile and wood type laminate flooring throughout. This home features a forced heating and cooling system, in addition to 2 evaporative coolers & solar system, to save on utility costs. It is closely located near the Mojave airport, PP&G and Edwards Airforce base, and is central to many larger cities.
